caption.title: Fig S2. AUC Jackknife analysis.
caption.p: AUC Jackknife analysis for the environmental variables used in the current distribution models generation of L. guanicoe (LG) and its lineage in Chile (LGC = L.g. cacsilensis; LGG = L.g. guanicoe; MP = Mixed population). The variables are Bio1 = Annual mean temperature; Bio4 = Temperature seasonality; Bio7 = Temperature annual range; Bio12 = Annual precipitation Bio15 = Precipitation seasonality.
